title: SetTime Appointment Scheduler

creator: We-Construct LLC
descriptionHtml:
Introducing SetTime Appointment Scheduler - Your Free Ultimate Solution for Efficient Appointment Booking!

SetTime is an online multifunctional appointment scheduling software that connects customers with service providers, making the process of booking faster and more organized.
Request and confirm online booking 24/7 and stay organized with a Free online booking calendar.
Set, confirm, cancel, and reschedule appointments in a few clicks, and make customer appointment scheduling easy.


Key Features:
- Staff & Customer Management: Manage all your customers and staff information in one centralized location for easy access and reference.

- Notification & Reminders: Never miss an appointment again with automatic reminders sent via email, ensuring a smooth experience for both parties.

- Online Booking Link: Let your clients book appointments directly through your social media pages or website, streamlining the booking process.

- Real-time Statistics: Gain valuable insights into your appointments, staff, and services with comprehensive real-time statistics.

- Time Zones: SetTime Appointment Scheduler automatically detects time zones, making it a breeze to schedule appointments across different regions.

Industries We Serve:
SetTime is designed to cater to the needs of businesses and individuals across a wide range of industries. Whether you’re in Beauty, SPA, Pet Care, Cleaning, Car Wash, Health, or any other sector, our app is tailored to meet your specific requirements.

Customizable Services:
Create custom services tailored to your specific needs and preferences, making your scheduling process even more personalized.

Auto Accept & Buffer Time:
Streamline your operations with the Auto Accept feature, eliminating the need for communication to confirm bookings. Add Buffer Time to reduce customer wait times and enhance overall service quality.

Booking Link - Your Gateway to Seamless Appointments:
Our Booking Link feature is the backbone of effortless scheduling. Share the Booking Link with your customers, making it a breeze for them to book appointments with just one click. Display your free QR code on leaflets, adverts, and storefronts for added convenience.

Custom Booking Link:
Personalize your Booking Link to reflect your brand identity and make it more memorable for your clients.

Efficient Customer and Staff Management:
Adding new customers and staff members is quick and easy. For those with extensive contact lists, the Import From Contacts feature simplifies adding multiple customers at once.

Track Your Progress with Detailed Statistics:
Keep an eye on your appointment statistics, staff performance, and most-booked services to make informed business decisions and drive growth.

Join SetTime Appointment Scheduler today and experience the ease of appointment scheduling like never before! Get started for free with no credit card required. Download now and unlock a new era of seamless booking for your business.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Some exciting updates to share with you!

・Improved user experience.
・Bug fixes for better performance and stability.
